      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037621&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5437&rangeEnd=5474",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3fd321c0813ab7532g0112a3?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5437&rangeEnd=5474"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037621_3_42505-42558",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "42505-42558",
      "markText": "我总是习惯先对事物进行深入骨髓的分析，再慢慢悠悠地想出万全之策。当然，过于强调万无一失，往往导致错失良机。",
      "totalCount": 442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037621&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=42505&rangeEnd=42558",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3fd321c0813ab7532g0112a3?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=42505&rangeEnd=42558"
    },
    {
